Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As we live our days just like the stormy seas{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.90,0:00:33.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}migi mo hidari mo guchagucha \Nni areta umi no youna jidai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even the values we had built \Nup were about to fall apart{\i0}
