Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:09.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}iza te wo nobashite kaze wo kirisaite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kick away the darkness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:14.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kurayami wo kettobashite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I do it for my own{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ima boku wa boku no tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you do yours, don't we?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:22.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kimi wa kimi no tame ni sou darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw your own map{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:26.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}onore no chizu wo egaite yuke{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure that you had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the Gum power is affecting\Nthings other than your own body...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can assume\Nyour Paramythia has awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of transformation...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is an exclusive feature of Zoan type!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.17,0:02:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy obtains a new power\Nand challenges Kaido again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They both exceeded their limits,\Nbut the deadly battle continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong with him?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Turning himself white,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and using both Color of Arms and\NColor of the Supreme King,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he's fighting so freely\Naffecting things other than his own body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never seen something like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll surpass you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.88,0:03:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"No Way Out!\NA Hellish Scene on Onigashima"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to know that\Nyou're still impudent, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your mind and body\Ncatch up to your power, Awakening occurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How ridiculous your power is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already lost so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost so much of what I've built.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boeuf Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly away, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King of Hell, Three-Sword Serpent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,103 Mercies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon Damnation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra Large Imperial Flaming Wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My subordinates and the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, there are things\NI have to take back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll lose more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I will take more from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kundali Dragon Swarm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The floors and the castle\Nare all on fire below.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure thousands of your soldiers\Nare stuck there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll all burn to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate them, Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything below in their hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...focus on kicking your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you laugh annoys me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demolition Gust!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It almost hit my crotch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:56.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PERFORMANCE FLOOR INSIDE THE DOME
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:09:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just the castle anymore!\NAll the towers are burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.41,0:09:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otama, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone protected me,\Nso I was only slightly wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat your wounds later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?\NThe fire can't be put out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, Sanji, Franky, Brook,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, Robin, and Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find any of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're in the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if we tried to find them,\Nthe whole of Onigashima is on fire now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not safe here, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless it lands, we have nowhere to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeus, can't you use your rain\Nto put out the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire is too intense,\NI would get burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all worked so hard\Nto get to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so frustrating\Nto see it end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't worry!\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be all right,\Nso don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to see Big Bro Luffy win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:27.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BASEMENT INSIDE THE CASTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't escape! The fire's everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:46.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRST FLOOR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving us too much trouble, Bepo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this really is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we can get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:08.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BASEMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My precious afro is getting frizzier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.21,0:11:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah! I don't want to end up like you.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're frustrated!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you!\NI don't know what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for you... You must have\Nfailed to escape and got burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a burnt corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am dead though...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's burning intensely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's no way for all of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:02.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FOURTH FLOOR INSIDE THE CASTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I can't die just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.\NI like helping people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was extremely lucky to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in on your secret plan with pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my {\i1}ninjutsu{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,now is the time to salvage this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, endure it a little bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These loathsome flames...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put them all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PLEASURE HALL, LEFT-BRAIN TOWER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.83,0:13:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. We can't get outside\Nbecause the yard is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An abyss in front...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a hellish fire behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even turn back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'll protect you ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're in the air,\Nso there's no place to go...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fire and the collapse\Nand the ladies...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:51.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BASEMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining that it's hot!\NBreak the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay here, we're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just sacrifice one of your damn arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That big body's so useless, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna fight, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,BASEMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heat and the flames\Nhave us backed in a corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way for us to survive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.23,0:14:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we knew that,\Nwe wouldn't be having a hard time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna die from the heat\Nif nothing's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do something, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna put out this fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack Green Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sprinkler!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what\N"a drop in the bucket" means, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I gotta figure out a way!\NI promised Izo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna save Kin and Kiku,\Nand myself as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! Please include me in that list!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't depend on me!\NYou have to save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,RIGHT-BRAIN TOWER
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The castle is burning ridiculously!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for us, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro's life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take him to Chopper\Nas soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all gonna get burned to death\Nbefore that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot! It's hot! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help us, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's whining?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna burn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:12.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THIRD FLOOR INSIDE THE CASTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dead end again! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flames and the debris\Nkeep getting the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone go around\Nand set fires?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way I'm gonna be killed\Nby fire and not by the enemy in a raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a fight is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna get defeated by fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.41,0:16:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:44.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FOURTH FLOOR INSIDE THE CASTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready, Jimbei-{\i1}dono{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for trusting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy chose to form an alliance\Nwith you samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd doubt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm trusting you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was ready since that day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.78,0:17:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toki-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't save Oden-{\i1}sama{\i0} that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I let Momonosuke-{\i1}sama {\i0}and the others\Nsuffer in the burning castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I could use {\i1}ninjutsu{\i0},\NI couldn't save anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a big blunder that I regret!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never ever want...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.77,0:17:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to feel that way again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogstorm, what kind of rain is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zunesha is bathing itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lot of water! May I take some?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let\Nthose who took part in this raid die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in this damn fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that it took so long, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you the incredible water flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninpo: Scrolling Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Elephant's Bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Restoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is enormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish-Man Jiu-Jitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean Current Shoulder Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run through every part of the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it in time and save everyone,\NZou's water!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:46.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FIRST FLOOR INSIDE THE CASTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me down, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to let us do this for you\Nat least, Killer-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!\NThere really is nowhere to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.28,0:20:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a rumble...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Momonosuke-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Kaido is still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to sustain the island\Nwith your Flame Clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sustain the island? That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido is reaching his limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Flame Clouds won't last much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must create Flame Clouds\Nto sustain Onigashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only option\Nfrom the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, Onigashima will fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Time's up"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:08.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"jikan gire sa"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone laughed again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.37,0:22:12.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}dareka ga mata waratta{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, now hide-and-seek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:17.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}joutou saa kakurenbo wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is over{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:19.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}owari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go, come on\N(We can see it soon){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:24.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}ikou hora\N(mou sugu mieru){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Make our hearts beat loudly\N(Our island){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:28.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}kodoku nari kishimase\N(boku tachi no shima ga){\i0}
