Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:09.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}issho nara ikeru Fly{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.64,0:23:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Bartolomeo, will tell you all about\Nthe bravery of Luffy-senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who is in a fierce battle\Nagainst the Emperor of the Sea Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get to see so much of\NBig Bro Luffy's heroic actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.36,0:23:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy-senpai Support Project!\NBarto's Secret Room 3!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.95,0:23:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-senpai's gonna become\Nthe King of the Pirates!
